title: Ant-Bee Discography
description:
The complete discography of Billy James' psychedelic music project Ant-Bee. His music married The Beach Boys' eccentric arrangements with Frank Zappa's humor and Pink Floyd's experimentation. In later releases he absorbed cosmic music and space rock into his kaleidoscope of sounds. Ant-Bee's albums feature many of the greatest players in rock and roll history, such as: Captain Beefheart's Magic Band (Zoot Horn Rollo, Rockette Morton, Richard Snyder), The Mothers of Invention (Bunk Gardner, Jim Sherwood, Roy Estrada, Jimmy Carl Black), Napoleon Murphy Brock (Zappa), Daevid Allen and Gilli Smyth (Gong), Harvey Bainbridge (Hawkwind), Alice Cooper Band (Michael Owen Bruce, Glen Edward Buxton, Neal Smith, Dennis Dunaway), Moogy Klingman (Todd Rundgren's band), Peter Banks (Yes), Jan Akkerman (Focus) and Bruce Cameron.

contains: 
(1990) Pure Electric Honey
(1994) Ant-Bee With My Favorite ''Vegetables'' and Other Bizarre Muzik
(1997) Lunar Muzik
(2010) Electronic Church Muzik
